	<tr>
		<td style="font-family: Trebuchet MS; font-size: 8pt; color: #FFFFFF; font-weight: bold; text-align: left; background-color: #333333; border-left: 2px solid #000000; border-right: 2px solid #FFFFFF; border-top: 2px solid #000000; border-bottom: 2px solid #FFFFFF">
          		<br><u><i><font color="#FFFF00">MISC CODES:</font></i></u><br>
			&nbsp; Hidden Bowling Game -
                  &nbsp; <font color="#00FF00">To unlock hidden bowling, you must get into two-player mode and both players must be Armadon. Both players must perform the Spinning Death move three times at the same time. If done right, both players and their human worshippers will walk offscreen for a bowling game.</font>&nbsp;
			<br>&nbsp; Hidden Volleyball Game -
                  &nbsp; <font color="#00FF00">To unlock this game, get into two-player mode and select Sauron's stage. Have a player complete a combo. Two humans will appear and start to bow. The player closest to the human must knock the human into the air and the other player has to hit him in the air before he reaches the ground. Continue volleying until a net and a judge appear.</font>&nbsp;
			<br>&nbsp; Alternate Character Colors -
                  &nbsp; <font color="#00FF00">When selecting your character, highlight the character of your choice and press X and either Circle, Square, or Triangle.</font>&nbsp;<br><br>
	 </tr>
	</table>
